{{ 'community-styles.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="community-section">
  <div class="community-background">
    {%- if section.settings.background_image -%}
      {{ section.settings.background_image | image_url | img_tag: 'Background Image', 'background-image' }}
    {%- else -%}
      <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0585/5261/4994/files/BlackRabbit.png?v=1759767102"
          alt="Black Rabbit Background"
          class="background-image"
      >
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <div class="community-content">
    <h1 class="community-title">{{ section.settings.title | default: "THE APEX ALLIANCE: Your Inner Circle" }}</h1>
    <p class="community-subtitle">{{ section.settings.subtitle | default: "The work is solitary, but the victory is shared." }}</p>

    <div class="community-intro">
      <p>You didn't reach this point by following the crowd. You forged your own path, fueled by a deep, quiet ambition. Black Rabbit.club is not just a brand; it's an alliance built for that specific drive. We are the inner circle of the relentless—a community where mastery is the only currency that matters.</p>
      <p class="highlight">Your membership is the key to mastering your second chapter.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="why-join">
      <h2>1. WHY JOIN THE ALLIANCE?</h2>
      <p>We don't sell products; we provide the edge. Our community is designed to eliminate friction, amplify performance, and reward the pursuit of excellence.</p>
      
      <div class="comparison-table">
        <div class="table-header">
          <div class="col">The Problem</div>
          <div class="col">The Alliance Solution</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="col">Identity Drift (Mid-Life Catalyst)</div>
          <div class="col">Access to The Blueprint: Exclusive content on long-term financial mastery, health protocols, and lifestyle efficiency.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="col">No Leverage (Missing Exclusivity)</div>
          <div class="col">Priority Launch Access: Be the first to secure every new product drop (like the 'Apex' Watch Set) with 48-hour pre-order windows and members-only pricing.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="col">Lack of Utility (Generic Perks)</div>
          <div class="col">Local Alliances: Tangible perks like discounts on premium gym memberships and invitations to exclusive biker forum events in metro cities.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pillars">
      <h2>2. THE THREE PILLARS OF MASTERY</h2>
      <p>Your membership provides real-world value across the three essential areas of high performance:</p>

      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>I. THE VAULT (Exclusive Access)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Early Product Drops: Guarantee your place in our limited-edition product runs.</li>
          <li>The Mark of the Rabbit: Exclusive member pricing for replacement bands, custom accessories, and watch maintenance services.</li>
          <li>Community Rewards: Entry into exclusive member-only draws and lottery-style offers that reward loyalty and engagement.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>II. THE BLUEPRINT (Knowledge & Focus)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Actionable Intelligence: Direct-to-inbox newsletter providing non-fluff intelligence on sustained high performance, goal setting, and mental fortitude—delivered in the sharp, unyielding voice of the Black Rabbit.</li>
          <li>Exclusive Surveys: Shape the future of the brand by voting on new product designs, materials, and features.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar">
        <h3>III. THE NETWORK (Real-World Utility)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Wellness Alliances: Partnerships with high-end fitness and health providers to sustain your physical edge.</li>
          <li>Local Meets & Events: Invitations to curated Alliance gatherings that connect you with fellow leaders and entrepreneurs in your city.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>SECURE YOUR ACCESS.</h2>
      <p>The greatest value we offer is clarity of purpose. Stop seeking success. Start defining mastery.</p>
      <p>Join the Alliance now to unlock your benefits and begin forging your legacy.</p>
      
      <form class="signup-form" action="/account/register" method="post">
        <input type="email" name="customer[email]" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
        <input type="password" name="customer[password]" placeholder="Create password" required>
        <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Join The Alliance</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Community Section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "background_image",
      "label": "Background Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "THE APEX ALLIANCE: Your Inner Circle"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subtitle",
      "default": "The work is solitary, but the victory is shared."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Community Section",
      "category": "Custom Sections"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}